5. ⚠️ Common mistakes (this is likely your issue)

❌ Using wrong URL

Wrong:

/alfresco/service/...

Correct:

/share/proxy/alfresco/...

⸻

❌ Expecting renderProperty to call API

It will never call backend.

⸻

❌ Missing XHR service in page

If service is not declared → nothing happens

⸻

❌ Topic mismatch

If you publish:

LOAD_MESSAGE

But subscribe to:

LOAD-MESSAGE

→ nothing will fire

